05:50.250 --> 05:53.150
I think I gotta
save your ass one more time.

05:53.190 --> 05:57.880
Take Tampa Bay on the money line.
They're gonna win this game outright.

05:57.910 --> 05:59.720
- Bet 'em big.
- Thanks B.

05:59.760 --> 06:03.830
