on pro football Sunday

06:40.320 --> 06:42.890
and hit my third straight
Monday-night parlay.

06:42.930 --> 06:46.790
- It's worth 12 bucks an hour.
- Hey I don't make 12 an hour.

06:46.820 --> 06:49.040
You're not picking 75%.

06:49.080 --> 06:52.420
If you're that good why don't you
bet your own games get rich?

