09:49.100 --> 09:50.380
A long time.

09:50.430 --> 09:53.510
- Two weeks.
- Two weeks.

09:53.550 --> 09:56.580
Every day with Walter's an adventure.

09:56.610 --> 09:58.410
Super cool, super mean

09:58.460 --> 10:02.170
Feelin' good for the man,
supertly, here I stand

