how'd you get the yacht?

14:06.460 --> 14:08.320
There's no yacht.

14:08.360 --> 14:10.190
Next question.

14:10.290 --> 14:15.300
Why give any picks for free?
Why not charge a fee up-front initially?

14:15.330 --> 14:17.810
You make a good point. Next.

14:17.850 --> 14:20.260
What's on the second floor?

14:20.300 --> 14:23.320
That's where we print the money.

14:24.160 --> 14:27.250
- Anything else?
- Of course not.

14:27.290 --> 14:31.300
No I think I've got it.
I think everything's crystal clear Walter.

14:31.330 --> 14:35.320
I like you you know that?
You and me - this thing's gonna work.

14:36.880 --> 14:38.760
- I'm looking forward to it.
