15:01.210 --> 15:03.010
- Brandon?
- Yeah.

15:03.050 --> 15:04.930
- Hi. I'm Toni.
- Nice to meet you.

15:04.960 --> 15:06.980
Walter said you'd stop by.

15:07.020 --> 15:09.370
- This was his idea.
- Yeah I know.

15:09.420 --> 15:11.920
Does he make
all of his employees do this?

15:11.950 --> 15:14.280
- Yep. Every one.
- How often?

15:14.320 --> 15:16.610
