15:40.520 --> 15:43.410
- I asked do you bet? Are you a bettor?
- No.

15:43.720 --> 15:45.550
Really?

15:45.580 --> 15:47.370
Why not?

15:48.310 --> 15:50.610
Toni huh?

15:52.270 --> 15:56.450
- Are you here full time?
- Yeah no this is my shop. I better be.

15:56.480 --> 15:58.800
So why don't you gamble?

15:58.840 --> 16:03.430
Well I did once.
I wagered everything I had and I lost.

16:03.460 --> 16:04.640
So?

16:04.680 --> 16:07.670
I just swore I'd never do it again.

16:07.710 --> 16:09.860
- You're sticking to that story?
- Yeah.

16:09.900 --> 16:12.670
