17:23.859 --> 17:25.770
Your bedroom.

17:25.810 --> 17:29.780
Got a Jacuzzi in there
the size of a kiddy pool.

17:30.920 --> 17:34.360
You know what this is?
Looks like weights to me.

17:34.400 --> 17:36.410
Yeah baby.

17:36.450 --> 17:39.890
